#CHIP C352
#CLOCK 16000000

; C352 (Namco System 21/22) Filter Test
;
; The C352 includes a digital filter that can be applied to PCM channels.
; This test validates filter parameter sweep and frequency response.
;
; Tests:
; - Low-pass filter sweep
; - High-pass filter sweep  
; - Filter cutoff frequency accuracy
; - Resonance behavior

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; Start with no filter (bypass)
c4 . . .

; Apply low-pass filter, sweep cutoff from low to high
c4 . d4 . e4 .

r4

; Apply high-pass filter, sweep cutoff from high to low
g4 . f4 . e4 . d4 .

r4

; Filter with resonance
c4 _ _ _

r4

; Rapid filter modulation
c4 . d4 . e4 . f4 . g4 . a4 .

r2

#END
